{"ts":"2026-06-26T13:32:27.757Z","author":"claude-code-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-xsth"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"CodeFactor/Maintainability: remove useless object-spread fallbacks (unicorn/no-useless-fallback-in-spread ×57)"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"**Rule:** `eslint-plugin-unicorn` / `no-useless-fallback-in-spread`. **Count:** 57 (Maintainability, Minor).\n\n**CodeFactor list:** https://www.codefactor.io/repository/github/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/main?category=Maintainability&groupId=10573\n\n## What it is\n\nSpreading `null`/`undefined` into an **object literal** is a no-op, so a `|| {}` / `?? {}` fallback is dead code:\n\n```ts\n{ ...(context ?? {}) }   // ->  { ...context }\n```\n\n## Confirmed instances (grep; verify each is an OBJECT spread)\n\n- `src/cli/main.ts:344`, `src/cli/main.ts:385` — `...(context ?? {})`\n- `src/cli/help-json-payload.ts:334` — `...(runtimeContext ?? {})`\n- `src/cli/help-content.ts:892`\n- `src/cli/commands/test.ts:1227` — `...(linkedTest.env_set ?? {})`\n- ~57 total across `src/**` — see the CodeFactor list for the complete set.\n\n## Important caveat\n\nThe rule applies to **object** spread only. **Array** spread `[...(x ?? [])]` is NOT useless — spreading `undefined` into an array throws — so do NOT strip `?? []` fallbacks. Only remove `?? {}` / `|| {}` inside object literals.\n\n## Fix\n\nLargely auto-fixable (`eslint --fix` once the parity lint exists — see sibling tooling item). Apply, then confirm tests + 100% coverage + typecheck stay green."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Chore"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":3},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["code-quality","codefactor","eslint","good-first-issue","maintainability"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-06-26T13:32:27.757Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-26T13:32:27.757Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"claude-code-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"CodeFactor reports 0 no-useless-fallback-in-spread findings; full coverage suite (node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage) stays green at 100%; pnpm typecheck and quality gates pass."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-92if"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"d4935248cc041af51c703cb25afa11aff9085d889b6753ca2a860cc01b07fcef","message":""}
